Laura Ann CANCIO n/k/a Laura Ann Davis, Appellant,
v.
Juan Manuel CANCIO, Appellee. No. 3D18-345 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. Opinion filed February 20, 2019 Law Offices of Robin Bresky, and Robin Bresky and Jeremy Dicker (Boca Raton), for appellant. Juan Manuel Cancio, in proper person. Before FERNANDEZ, LOGUE, and LINDSEY, JJ. PER CURIAM.

Finding the issues raised in the current appeal virtually identical to the issues raised by appellant in her prior appeal which was affirmed, Cancio v. Cancio , Case No. 17-2774, 2018 WL 2230038 (Fla. 3d DCA May 16, 2018), we affirm here as well.

Affirmed.
